    "Similarly, for Block, demonstration videos use target regions with randomly varying colors and positions.",
    "Human→Robot (no target-robot data).",
    "We fine-tuneTraceGen with five uncalibrated human demonstrations (handheld phone, different scene) to adapt trace predictions to the target task; no target-robot demonstrations are used.",
    "Each video is only 3-4 seconds long, and a single person performing the task while another records it is sufficient to obtain the data.",
